<plot>Cinderella and her family live mid 20th century, where fashion is practically everything. As her father is won over by a selfish woman named Claudette, Cinderella must keep her new step-mother from murdering the only family she has left. Add in an anti-social fairy literally living in a cave, a bored prince with an ear for rock n' roll, and the glamor of the 1950's and one'll find that this story can't grow old.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?106398</url></doc>
